  "content": "<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" style=\"font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif\"> \n<head>\n  <title>Supplier Master Data Submission Status</title>\n     <style>\n        table {\n            width: 80%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n        th, td {\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            padding: 8px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        th {\n            background-color: #f2f2f2;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n       .right-aligned-table {\n   \t\t \tfloat: right;\n    \t\tmargin-left: 15px; /* Adds some space between the table and text */\n  \t\t}\n    </style>\n </head> \n <body>\n\n   <h4>Hello Team,</h4>\n   <n></n>\n   <n><t>We have encountered validation errors during processing of this request for Ariba Supplier -<b> {{ VendorID }}. </b></t></n>\n   <n></n>\n   <h4> Summary of the Issue - </h4>\n    <table>\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th>S/N</th>\n                <th>Supplier</th>\n                <th>Site Name</th>\n                <th>Error Message</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody> \n           {{#Rows}}\n            <tr>\n              \t<td>  {{ SerialNo }} </td>\n              \t<td>  {{ VendorName }} </td>\n              \t<td>  {{ VendorSiteCode }} </td>\n                <td>  {{ InterfaceError }} </td>\n            </tr>\n\t\t\t{{/Rows}}\n        </tbody>\n\t</table>\n   <n>IT Team is currently reviewing this validation error. </n>\n   <n>Please contact the IT Support Team if you have urgent questions regarding this request.</n>\n   <div/>\n   <h4>Best Regards,</h4>\n   <n>IT Team</n>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
